transactionCategory.description:
The category of the transaction.
 SALE_OR_RETURN - are transaction that deals with sale or return of items.
 CONTROL - this transaction mainly deals with non-monetary related transactions like Cashier checking in to a POS.
 CASH_OFFICE - deals with movement of money from one location to another. 
 APEX_TRANSACTION - transaction that captures travel information. 
 TANK_FUEL_READING_TRANSACTION - transaction that captures information related to Tank readings. 
 PUMP_FUEL_READING_TRANSACTION - transaction that captures information related to Pump readings. 
 FUEL_DELIVERY_TRANSACTION - transaction that captures information related to Tank deliveries. 
PUMP_FUEL_TEST_TRANSACTION - transaction captures information related to Pump testing and calibrations. 
CUSTOM_TRANSACTION - A custom transaction that can represent transactions from POS that are not 
represented by other transaction categories. Contains data that is not part of TDM model and that is custom to each data provider.
STORED_VALUE_TRANSACTION - Stored Value Transaction Information associated with the Transaction.
